<br>
Summary <br>
Meet at BB docks at 7pm<br>
Catch boat out to the Island<br>
Take Siren out (lvl 15ish)<br>
Take Brawn out (lvl 22ish)<br>
<br>
Maybe's<br>
Take out the 2 Dragoons (lvl 22ish)<br>
