Head to Freeport and have a few drinks at the Tavern and chat about our days adverture.<br>
<br>
All the best<br>
Goladar <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/ugoladarthebrave.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goladar the Brave</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#8B4513>(4/1/01 9:02:57 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.fbe.unsw.edu.au/staff/Marko.Furschke/Golihead.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Falchion of Koada'vie</span><hr size=1> Hey there guys<br>
